trans-unit.source: JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter merges navigation back history and navigation forward history (as exposed by <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref>) into a single, [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style navigation menu.
trans-unit.target: 뒤로 탐색 기록 및 앞으로 탐색 기록 JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter 병합 (로 노출 <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> 또는 <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"> </xref>)을 단일 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-스타일 탐색 메뉴.

trans-unit.source: Both <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> display navigation chrome that supports history navigation using the following mechanisms: - A button for navigating back one piece of content at a time.
trans-unit.target: 둘 다 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>및 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>다음과 같은 메커니즘을 사용 하 여 기록 탐색을 지 원하는 탐색 크롬 표시:-를 탐색 하기 위한 단추 한 번에 한 콘텐츠를 백업 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: - A button for navigating forward one piece of content at a time.
trans-unit.target: -앞으로 탐색 콘텐츠의 한 번에 대 한 단추입니다.

trans-unit.source: - An [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list that shows: - A combined list of up to nine items in back navigation history and up to nine items in forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: -An [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-보여 주는 스타일 드롭 다운 목록:-최대&9; 개의의 결합 된 목록의 항목 뒤에 탐색 기록 및 앞으로 탐색 기록의 항목으로 구성 합니다.

trans-unit.source: - The position of the current piece of content with respect to both back and forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: -뒤로 및 앞으로 탐색 기록 둘 다에 대해 콘텐츠는 현재 데이터의 위치입니다.

trans-unit.source: The navigation history is stored by both <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> in the following properties: **Back Navigation History**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 탐색 기록 둘 다로 저장 된 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>다음과 같은 속성으로: **뒤로 탐색 기록**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: **Forward Navigation History**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: **탐색 기록 전달**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To create the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> use JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter to merge their individual back navigation history and forward navigation history into a single list of navigation history entries.
trans-unit.target: 만들려는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-스타일 드롭 다운 목록 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter를 사용 하 여 병합의 개별 뒤로 탐색 기록 앞으로 탐색 기록의 탐색을 단일 목록으로 기록 항목을.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: The resulting list contains up to nine entries from back navigation history and up to nine entries from forward navigation history, plus an entry for the current content.
trans-unit.target: 결과 목록 항목이&9; 개까지 뒤로 탐색 기록에서 및 최대&9; 개의 항목 앞으로 탐색 기록에서 및 현재 내용에 대 한 항목이 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: If you create custom navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], and need to provide an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list, you can use JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter to similar effect.
trans-unit.target: 사용자 지정 탐색을 만들면 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]를 제공 해야 할는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-스타일 드롭 다운 목록 JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter를 사용 하면 비슷한 효과 얻을 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: Merges two navigation history stacks.
trans-unit.target: 두 탐색 기록 스택을 병합합니다.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, the navigation stacks are available from the following properties: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A> For <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, the navigation stacks are available from the following properties: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A> The two passed navigation stacks are combined into a single navigation stack that contains up to nine items from each navigation stack plus the current item.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, 탐색 스택은 다음 속성에서 사용할 수 있는:- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A>에 대 한 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, 탐색 스택은 다음 속성에서 사용할 수 있는:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A><xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A>두 전달 된 탐색 스택의 현재 항목 함께 각 탐색 스택에서&9; 개까지 항목을 포함 하는 단일 탐색 스택을로 결합 됩니다.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>
